  <summary date="2015-02-24T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Trust Returned to the United States Taxpayer Act or the TRUST Act

Denies retirement benefits under the Civil Service Retirement System and the Federal Employees Retirement System to a Member of Congress who is convicted of any crime committed after the enactment of this Act&#160;that is a felony under federal or state law (currently, limited to specified felonies under federal law).</summary>
